      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/3592" title="Spring Security 3.1.1 Released">Spring Security 3.1.1 Released</a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by rwinch on Fri, 2012-07-06 19:35        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_4 first last"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4" rel="tag" title="News and announcements
">News and Announcements</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>We're pleased to an announce the GA release of Spring Security 3.1.1<br />
The release is available from the <a href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=Spring%20Security">Spring Community Downloads area</a> and jars are available from Maven central repository. See the <a href="http://www.springsource.org/spring-security">project website</a> for more information.</p>
<p><a href="https://jira.springsource.org/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10040&amp;version=12705">Changelog</a> | <a href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=Spring%20Security&amp;version=3.1.1.RELEASE">Download</a> | <a href="http://static.springsource.org/spring-security/site/docs/3.1.x/reference/springsecurity-single.html">Reference Manual</a> | <a href="http://static.springsource.org/spring-security/site/faq.html">FAQ</a></p>
